---
const stats = [
  { value: "5+", label: "TAHUN PENGALAMAN" },
  { value: "50+", label: "PROJECT SELESAI" },
  { value: "30+", label: "CLIENT PUAS" }
];
---

<section class="hero-section min-h-screen flex items-center pt-20 border-b-[8px] border-black bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Decorative Elements -->
  <div class="hero-deco-1 absolute top-32 right-12 w-24 h-24 border-[4px] border-black opacity-20"></div>
  <div class="hero-deco-2 absolute bottom-20 left-8 w-16 h-16 bg-[#0058be] opacity-10"></div>
  <div class="hero-deco-3 absolute top-1/2 right-1/4 w-2 h-32 bg-black opacity-5"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 w-full">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="hero-badge">
          <span class="inline-block font-mono text-xs font-bold tracking-widest bg-black text-white px-4 py-2 mb-8">CREATIVE DEVELOPER</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="font-display text-5xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-extrabold leading-[0.95] tracking-tight mb-8">
          <span class="hero-name-block">
            <span class="hero-name-text inline-block">SINDU</span>
          </span><br/>
          <span class="hero-name-block">
            <span class="hero-name-text text-[#0058be] inline-block">ADITYA</span>
          </span>
        </h1>

        <p class="hero-desc font-body text-lg md:text-xl text-[#424754] max-w-xl mb-10 leading-relaxed">
          Membangun pengalaman digital yang bold dan fungsional. Fokus pada high-performance interfaces dengan aesthetic neo-brutalist yang gak takut untuk stand out.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-buttons flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="#work" class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#0058be] text-white px-8 py-4 font-mono text-sm font-bold border-[4px] border-black shadow-[6px_6px_0_0_#000] hover:shadow-[8px_8px_0_0_#000] hover:-translate-x-1 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200">
            LIHAT PROJECT
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-[#1a1c1c] px-8 py-4 font-mono text-sm font-bold border-[4px] border-black hover:bg-[#f3f3f3] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-200">
            HUBUNGI SAYA
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Stats -->
        <div class="hero-stats flex gap-8 mt-16 pt-8 border-t-[2px] border-black">
          {stats.map((stat) => (
            <div class="stat-item">
              <span class="stat-value font-display text-4xl font-extrabold">{stat.value}</span>
              <p class="font-mono text-xs text-[#727785] mt-1">{stat.label}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5 hero-avatar">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-[#e8e8e8] border-[4px] border-black relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="avatar-inner absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-32 h-32 mx-auto bg-[#dadada] border-[4px] border-black rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
                  <span class="font-display text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#727785]">SA</span>
                </div>
                <span class="font-mono text-xs text-[#727785]">JAKARTA, INDONESIA</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-16 h-16 bg-[#0058be] border-t-[4px] border-l-[4px] border-black"></div>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 w-full h-full bg-[#dadada] border-[4px] border-black -z-10"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>